1. *Zadnje* što želim je da se osećam usamljeno. (The last thing I want is to feel lonely.)
2. On je video *zadnje* dane svoje majke. (He saw his mother's last days.)
3. On je čuo *zadnju* reč od nje. (He heard her last word.)
4. U *zadnje* vreme on je bio pun energije. (Recently, he was full of energy.)
5. Moje *zadnje* iskustvo u inostranstvu je bilo vrlo zabavno. (My last experience abroad was very enjoyable.)